{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/Sierkinhane/CRNN_Chinese_Characters_Rec/issues/185","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/Sierkinhane/CRNN_Chinese_Characters_Rec","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/Sierkinhane/CRNN_Chinese_Characters_Rec/issues/185/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/Sierkinhane/CRNN_Chinese_Characters_Rec/issues/185/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/Sierkinhane/CRNN_Chinese_Characters_Rec/issues/185/events","html_url":"https://github.com/Sierkinhane/CRNN_Chinese_Characters_Rec/issues/185","id":573336713,"node_id":"MDU6SXNzdWU1NzMzMzY3MTM=","number":185,"title":"pytorch自带的ctc loss似乎存在bug，改成第三方的实现可解决loss Nan和训练不收敛问题","user":{"login":"flyindirt","id":24094190,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjI0MDk0MTkw","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/24094190?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/flyindirt","html_url":"https://github.com/flyindirt","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/flyindirt/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/flyindirt/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/flyindirt/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/flyindirt/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/flyindirt/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/flyindirt/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/flyindirt/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/flyindirt/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/flyindirt/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false},"labels":[{"id":1069924222,"node_id":"MDU6TGFiZWwxMDY5OTI0MjIy","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/Sierkinhane/CRNN_Chinese_Characters_Rec/labels/enhancement","name":"enhancement","color":"a2eeef","default":true,"description":"New feature or request"}],"state":"closed","locked":false,"assignee":null,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":2,"created_at":"2020-02-29T17:00:52Z","updated_at":"2021-01-11T06:15:07Z","closed_at":"2020-03-22T01:50:10Z","author_association":"NONE","active_lock_reason":null,"body":"我用的pytorch 1.2版，一开始用的是pytorch自带的ctc loss，训练中遇到了很多问题：1）训练了几个批次后，loss 为Nan，最后把批次大小改为1才能继续训练下去；2）用了RmsPop优化器，训练集loss下降才快起来，到了0.05以下，但是验证集准确率始终为0，且验证集loss在20以上（为了能看到效果，我把验证集改的跟训练集一样）。\r\n后来看到其他开源实现没有用pytorch自带的ctc loss，我试了一下，更换了第三方的ctc loss实现，结果发现效果一下子就出来了，每一个epoch，准确率都在上升。\r\n我用的第三方ctc loss的pytorch包装实现是  https://github.com/jpuigcerver/pytorch-baidu-ctc ，其中的第三方ctc从百度的https://github.com/baidu-research/warp-ctc 源码下载。\r\n直接编译会失败，参考编译百度ctc的解决办法（删除，改符号链接），可以编译成功。\r\nI experienced   this same issue and fixed it. The problem is that the ctc_entrypoint.cu file   needs to be a symlink. So, go to src dir and run:   \r\nrm ctc_entrypoint.cu   \r\nln -s ctc_entrypoint.cpp ctc_entrypoint.cu  \r\n Then   run make.\r\n在pytorch1.2下，编译和安装成功。\r\n希望对大家有帮助。","closed_by":{"login":"Sierkinhane","id":41798797,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjQxNzk4Nzk3","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/41798797?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/Sierkinhane","html_url":"https://github.com/Sierkinhane","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Sierkinhane/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Sierkinhane/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Sierkinhane/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Sierkinhane/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Sierkinhane/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Sierkinhane/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Sierkinhane/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Sierkinhane/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Sierkinhane/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false},"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/Sierkinhane/CRNN_Chinese_Characters_Rec/issues/185/reactions","total_count":2,"+1":2,"-1":0,"laugh":0